Important Notes:

1. This code has been modified because the original code cannot be compiled.

2. Install ffmpeg BEFORE install OpenCV, otherwise you may encounter decoding issues.

3. There may be some dependencies for ffmpeg, such as yasm (http://yasm.tortall.net), pkg-config(http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/pkg-config/). Make sure you install ffmpeg successfully.

4. To compile the code: $ make 

5. To test the code: $ ./release/DenseTrackStab ./test_sequences/person01_boxing_d1_uncomp.avi -W 10

6. FOR LINUX PROBLEMS (follow this guide): http://www.ozbotz.org/opencv-installation/
